{"tid":1732912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港理大警民衝突 美官員：譴責不合理使用武力","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:59:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dfabaf6aadc1b189f4f2c2c21a9d911b0ccc38","tid":1732912,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓17日綜合外電報導）香港反送中示威者在理工大學與港警爆發激烈衝突，據報港警將他們困在理大。美國總統川普政府高階官員今天說，美國譴責港府「不合理使用武力」並呼籲北京保護香港民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，這名美國高階官員說：「我們譴責不合理使用武力，並敦促各方避免暴力行為，要展開建設性對話。」<br />\n<br />\n「正如總統先前所述，美國希望北京當局兌現中英聯合聲明中的承諾，保護香港自由、法治和民主的生活方式。」<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中示威者17日在理工大學與港警爆發激烈衝突，通宵對峙，校園內瀰漫催淚彈煙霧，各處失火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201911180048.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201911180048.aspx&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVhwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=2ee63a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201911180048.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"b889946ded3fe61d9a214f669edfa39a802bbc87","tid":1732912,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"5722970753fc8bc27532371943afc9540bebab69","tid":1732912,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"遣左半年"},{"pid":"ee3a4783184149f71b76fdab8f38b22c749b01d8","tid":1732912,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"譴責"},{"pid":"78ed0a85db708ed0cdc30b3e32f1b54689479ef8","tid":1732912,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【人道理由❗❗❗要求開路】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n##  一邊和你LUNCH，一邊要求開路呀!!! 推俾國際。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">街坊唔好講明去增援/開缺口，反而用❗人道理由❗要求開路</span>，運送食物+FA，<span style=\"color: red;\">要國際傳媒影住，popo唔俾，就加強我地國際線。</span>"},{"pid":"cd59d315dae64ecb004128bb26982695593ce3ac","tid":1732912,"uid":246141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"廢話。對依家有咩幫助？"},{"pid":"1f9301c720714cf373fe9073528b060612e77a59","tid":1732912,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"1. 要諗計射d 物資入去，班狗係寧願入面餓死哂都唔會開路。<br />\n2. 要用車，唔係乜都開始唔到。<br />\n3. 打得赢就班狗要end game。"},{"pid":"bd59e5ea557379bef2e18852914ab71b8ef70b10","tid":1732912,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"Bullshit"},{"pid":"b620778b1f3bedbd02ddde6c3c8949735b6ce5fe","tid":1732912,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"譴責"},{"pid":"4a054165e7294be3e0cd22a2ab67d6f3b54411fd","tid":1732912,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ZjRtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ZjRtg.jpg&h=edebd45e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n緊急呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去佐敦啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"a49cde485db53b540371ce4a2d103c916b95c7e4","tid":1732912,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"已閱"},{"pid":"b098997409197ffae5515708d6d42a2a5a045749","tid":1732912,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓17日綜合外電報導）香港反送中示威者在理工大學與港警爆發激烈衝突，據報港警將他們困在理大。美國總統川普政府高階官員今天說，美國譴責港府「不合理使用武力」並呼籲<span style=\"color: red;\">北京</span>保護香港民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n